products.name: Complete Fixed Home Loan Package
products.description: The Complete Fixed Home Loan Package includes a fixed home loan, up to 9 offset accounts, a credit card and other good stuff - including our great rates.

products.name: Fixed Rate Home Loan
products.description: The Fixed Rate Home Loan lets you lock in a competitive fixed rate for one to five years, and enjoy the peace of mind that comes with consistent repayments. The loan is available for both owner occupied and investment purposes (the loan amount will be restricted by your property value, repayment type and loan purpose). Plus link an optional offset facility to your loan to help reduce your interest and pay off your loan faster. After the expiry of your fixed rate term your Home Loan will revert to the Bankwest Simple Home Loan.

products.name: Bankwest Offset Transaction Account
products.description: For a less lazy home loan, pair an Offset Transaction Account with your eligible home loan, use it like an everyday bank or savings account, and you could save on your home loan interest.

products.name: Bankwest Smart eSaver
products.description: An online savings account that rewards you for every month you don't make a withdrawal. It's available to customers aged 12 years or over.

products.name: Hero Saver
products.description: A savings account that rewards you for making regular contributions and making no withdrawals. It's available to customers 12 years or over.

products.name: Retirement Advantage Account
products.description: The Retirement Advantage Account is for those aged 55 and over. Enjoy reduced fees and simple banking by combining a bank account and savings account in one.

products.name: Easy Transaction Account
products.description: Our Easy Transaction Account is our low fee bank account. With no monthly maintenance fee, you can make your money go further and easily manage your money.

products.name: Bankwest Qantas Transaction Account
products.description: A bank account that earns Qantas Points even when you're not flying. It's available to customers aged 18 years or over.

products.name: Bankwest Easy Saver
products.description: The Easy Saver Account is our flexible savings account that lets you earn interest on balances up to $250,000.99. With less BS (Bank Stuff) make withdrawals via your linked Bankwest Easy Transaction Account and no minimum monthly deposit.

products.name: AgriOne Account
products.description: A transaction account designed for primary producers, which combines with an Overdraft Facility (with a minimum credit limit of $100,000).

products.name: Real Estate Agent Trust - ACT
